MacOSX-File-XAttr version 0.01
==============================

Manipulate MacOS X extended file attributes from Perl without using
the xattr tool.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other modules outside of the core libraries.

